                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980110-37-defend382 t17980110-37-punish215"></join>
               fined 1s.
            </rs> and discharged.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
